      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled CFD solver with documented test suite covering hemolysis scalar transport; all regression tests pass.",
      "rationale": "The CFD package (OpenFOAM 9) is under version control with a documented regression test suite. All relevant solver tests pass. Achieved level meets required level for MRL 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
