      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests on canonical rotating-flow benchmark demonstrate expected second-order convergence for velocity and scalar fields.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to a rotating annular flow benchmark. Second-order spatial convergence confirmed for velocity components and hemolysis scalar. Achieved level meets required level."
