      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments performed on the same FDA generic pump geometry at operating conditions spanning the full COU envelope.",
      "rationale": "Validation used the FDA generic pump geometry. However, only three of five COU operating points were covered by bench experiments; the two highest-speed conditions were extrapolated. Achieved level (2) below required (3)."
    },
