    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Ten of thirteen credibility factors were assessed. Seven of the ten assessed factors achieved their required levels; three fell one grade below required. Three factors (Model form, Model inputs, Equivalency of input parameters) were left not-assessed as beyond current project scope. The team judged the assessed evidence sufficient to support a Low assurance level acceptance at MRL 3, noting that the not-assessed factors represent acknowledged epistemic gaps that do not materially affect the decision at this assurance level. No formal gap remediation plan is provided for the unassessed factors.",
